      <title>美联储会议前新兴市场资产利差上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/rally-in-emerging-market-assets-spreads-ahead-of-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储预计将于四年多来首次降息之前，新兴市场资产延续涨势，美元走软和美国国债收益率下降支撑了风险偏好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/rally-in-emerging-market-assets-spreads-ahead-of-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:33:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一系列坏消息令德国投资者信心暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/german-investor-confidence-plummets-after-spate-of-bad-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有进一步迹象表明德国制造业巨头面临越来越不确定的未来，投资者对德国经济的信心跌至近一年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/german-investor-confidence-plummets-after-spate-of-bad-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注鲍威尔能否效仿格林斯潘实现软着陆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/markets-hinge-on-powell-emulating-greenspan-s-soft-landing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们回想起 1995 年，当时艾伦·格林斯潘 (Alan Greenspan) 领导美联储实现了罕见的软着陆，并制定了四年来首次降息的策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/markets-hinge-on-powell-emulating-greenspan-s-soft-landing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Exane 称，收购爱马仕是为了应对奢侈品市场放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/hermes-a-defensive-trade-to-counter-luxury-slowdown-exane-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国巴黎银行证券部 (BNP Paribas Exane) 分析师表示，投资爱马仕国际 (Hermes International) 是投资者免受奢侈品行业短期低迷影响的一种方式，他们首次将这家铂金包制造商的评级上调至跑赢大盘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/hermes-a-defensive-trade-to-counter-luxury-slowdown-exane-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 08:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行民意调查显示，美联储押注自 6 月以来首次提振市场人气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/bofa-poll-says-fed-bets-lift-sentiment-for-first-time-since-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司的一项全球调查显示，对美联储备受期待的降息的乐观情绪自六月以来首次提振了投资者情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/bofa-poll-says-fed-bets-lift-sentiment-for-first-time-since-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 08:50:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔德国工厂推迟建设对欧盟芯片雄心造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/germany-faces-fresh-setback-as-intel-halts-planned-chip-factory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司决定推迟在德国建厂的计划，标志着欧盟半导体计划遭遇挫折，并将在柏林重新引发有关 100 亿欧元（110 亿美元）专项补贴该如何分配的争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/germany-faces-fresh-setback-as-intel-halts-planned-chip-factory</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 08:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储决议公布前油价持稳，但需求担忧依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球市场等待美联储本周普遍预期的降息，油价几乎没有变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 23:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要前，零售数据成为焦点，股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市和美国股指期货上涨，交易员期待最终一组经济数据，以便为美联储周三的降息规模提供线索。]]></description>
